    </span>
    <span class="flex items-center p-4 hover:bg-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 border-l-4 hover:border-gray-700"><button id="modal-register" class="btn font-bold">Regístrate / Mi cuenta</button></span> 
    <span class="flex items-center p-4 hover:bg-gray-300 hover:text-gray-900 border-l-4 hover:border-gray-700"><button id="modal-recommendations" class="btn font-bold">#QuédateEnCasa</button></span>
